snippet.title: Detective Kiwi - Trailer (HD)
snippet.description:
"Detective Kiwi" is a free to play multiplayer puzzle game that is designed for up to 6 players, featuring a simple rule: There will be 4 images every round. You need to find them as fast as you can.

Steam : https://store.steampowered.com/app/2744900/Detective_Kiwi/
Discord Server : https://discord.gg/SQNhRYrqZh
Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61555748902478
Reddit : https://www.reddit.com/r/DetectiveKiwi/
